name: Earl HARRIS, Petitioner v. David DIGUGLIELMO, Warden, Graterford State Prison, and Lynne Abraham, Phila. District Attorney, Respondents

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 14th day of April, 2009, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus Ad Subjiciendum is DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
